title: Hugars Quest
description: "The Adventures of Hugar" is an exciting game with a well-known mechanics of memory training method, in which you as a prince of the Northern Kingdom of Ice Golem Hugar must defend their land from invasion from the south. At our disposal are a variety of magical items to help in this extraordinary adventure. We will have to open the chests of gold, run away from a huge snowball fight with the soldiers, snowmen and much more. Nice cartoon graphics, lively music and an abundance of interesting levels will keep you entertained. Save your kingdom!
